{"tid":1287001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Block柒所有支持武漢撚","createTime":"2019-07-05T04:45:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T17:39:47.000Z","uid":56157,"like":175,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"095297e6ef40f4da9674a603c95bb84b540989f5","tid":1287001,"uid":56157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:45:02.000Z","msg":"好多五毛借兄弟爬山意圖令運動失焦。也有好多人已經中左招支持武漢<br />\n<br />\n要搞清楚兄弟爬山各自努力係講緊爬緊同一座山。即係有相同目的（反送中以及相關訴求）但唔會因為其手段（勇武/和理非）而割席<br />\n<br />\n武漢已經係第二座山。唔係爬同一座山點解要支持？<br />\n<br />\n有人話要文宣聲援，你要搞清楚人係有接受資訊既能力極限。每宣傳一次就會令人既接收能力少左。更何況反送中事件已開始降溫。呢個時候支持武漢只會令香港人訴求失焦。每一份武漢宣傳=減弱五大訴求傳<br />\n<br />\n有人話要借武漢黎提今日武漢明日香港，我1想講今日香港已經夠多例子。警察濫權亂拉亂打，白色恐怖。點解唔用返612等開槍鎮壓以及最近既白色恐怖以言入罪。材料咁多咁貼地仲要用武漢?<br />\n<br />\n也有人話要借武漢黎反共。反送中都係反共。<br />\n<br />\n請認清「支持武漢」對反送中訴求既破壞力。並block柒相關疑似五毛同盡量說服誤入岐途既人回正途"},{"pid":"66cbdda1806f5ad58b0e95a76c496ac206fc676c","tid":1287001,"uid":237528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:45:43.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"1d85e897a2c28f69658d5d30048712d2fccd0890","tid":1287001,"uid":200758,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:46:37.000Z","msg":"五毛可以用武漢分化我地，我地都可以利用武漢將把火燒上大陸，但記住唔係幫武漢，77當日要集中係五大訴求先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJfWtfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJfWtfJ.jpg&h=3b2d02f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6QrQt4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6QrQt4.jpg&h=02ad2ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ofWuem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ofWuem.png&h=f545a766&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a58c8a92a8dae7b9ddcf11c97a561c41c4c40b04","tid":1287001,"uid":65196,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:47:15.000Z","msg":"香港人要贏返香港"},{"pid":"025fcc5912414f6f615d015a696a1aa3b34af4f5","tid":1287001,"uid":174295,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:47:58.000Z","msg":"湖北琦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"575c9c8fcb70c9cfc282ae59f320fe2eac90f667","tid":1287001,"uid":56157,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:51:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f188a4a2ac07695193110356dfad6e1ad94d2c5c","tid":1287001,"uid":56157,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:54:15.000Z","msg":"小心滲透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a7e45d35e268e2ce6ec7a86347f6e890fe3c697","tid":1287001,"uid":109780,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:54:36.000Z","msg":"未至於要block, 提醒就得，不分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bc13058f195da088898541df21445976e79995a","tid":1287001,"uid":56157,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6a7e45d35e268e2ce6ec7a86347f6e890fe3c697","tid":1287001,"uid":109780,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:54:36.000Z","msg":"未至於要block, 提醒就得，不分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:55:22.000Z","msg":"盡左力但講極唔聽冇辦法。<br />\n<br />\n至少唔好幫佢地推"},{"pid":"a61b7113f1db67065c3e902867402bdcdd9994b3","tid":1287001,"uid":56157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:07:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b0b6ffab899a8f14c53f8e7f91d4b6af68ded3f","tid":1287001,"uid":270179,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:54:27.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">唔係好明點會有人張聲援武漢同分化反送中運動拉埋黎講\n分你老母，同路人對抗極權勢力，你唔撚撐？\n其他國家既事唔關你事，當初籌旗外國傳媒報g20 果時你唔咁講？\n而家好難得搵到個機會去抗大反共勢力\n撐武漢唔撚係分化，多個朋友好過多個敵人呀屌\n咪盲反中反上腦 鄰國仲有好多人係清醒既，咪比五毛分化到 五毛係好撚中意分化中港兩地人 張所有反抗極權既意向抹黑為分裂國家\n佢地最怕就係你地搞到中國人都識團結反抗\n\n要用腦，唔好下下一黎就盲反得唔得，連登風向太易帶\n\n重申重點：\n五大訴求當然唔可以失焦，但撐武漢絕對唔係分化</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好俾人分化到<br />\n冇人話要反攻大陸<br />\n只係要燒佢後欄<br />\n不割席<br />\n不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n1.撤回條例<br />\n2.釋放義士<br />\n3.取消暴動定性<br />\n4.追究警方濫用武力鎮壓<br />\n5.落實雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HtoEwdk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHtoEwdk.png&h=45ccf763&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Np0Z6F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Np0Z6F.png&h=d451cb32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/05/145107_1568e89c3160c354acbc9eda8c078eee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F05%2F145107_1568e89c3160c354acbc9eda8c078eee.png&h=2adf7012&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"758e62132f3fe90a8447267100bff4d951c61a9c","tid":1287001,"uid":61520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:55:52.000Z","msg":"幫手俾意見<br />\n<br />\n一人一信  no DQ  還我選舉權  <br />\n唔好比藉口人地將好的議員篩走<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://271467.typeform.com/to/MTUjKV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F271467.typeform.com%2Fto%2FMTUjKV&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BK3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=eaabf40c\" target=\"_blank\">https://271467.typeform.com/to/MTUjKV</a>"},{"pid":"a04f4aa7c27aeb6e07e9f3c67a69cdbc139719e2","tid":1287001,"uid":78349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"025fcc5912414f6f615d015a696a1aa3b34af4f5","tid":1287001,"uid":174295,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:47:58.000Z","msg":"湖北琦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T07:00:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一毛發現</span>"},{"pid":"69c18b17455f83b8629caeb2131ea62f0583bbf3","tid":1287001,